  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Development & Operations Executive (Payments / Fintech)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>8Hexa is a Singapore-based payment services company providing cross-border payment solutions to corporate clients and premium individuals. We are looking for a proactive Business Development & Operations Executive to support client acquisition and ensure smooth onboarding and transaction execution.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Identify and engage new corporate clients and business partners to expand the client base and drive business growth</li><li>Onboard new clients by coordinating with operations and compliance teams to ensure seamless and compliant transaction execution</li><li>Build and maintain strong client and partner relationships to foster long-term collaboration and trust</li><li>Assess client needs and recommend appropriate cross-border payment and FX solutions to meet their business objectives</li><li>Track and manage the sales pipeline and onboarding progress to provide timely updates and prepare basic performance reports</li><li>Represent the company at fintech events and networking sessions to enhance brand presence and generate new business opportunities</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Business, Finance, or related field (or equivalent experience)</li><li>Experience in business development, operations, fintech, or financial services</li><li>Knowledge of cross-border payments, FX, or B2B financial services</li><li>Strong communication and relationship-building skills demonstrated through client engagement and partnership development</li><li>Organised and self-motivated with the ability to work effectively in a regulated environment</li></ul>",
